{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "ecg-mgmt-api-collection",
		"name": "ECG Management API",
		"description": "API สำหรับเชื่อมต่อระบบ ECG Management กับระบบ รพ. (HIS)\n\n## Authentication\nใช้ API Key ส่งผ่าน Header `X-API-Key`\n\nดู API Key ได้ที่: Settings > General > API Integration\n\n## Setup\n1. แก้ไข Variable `base_url` ให้ตรงกับ server\n2. แก้ไข Variable `api_key` ให้ตรงกับ API Key ในระบบ",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:5000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "api_key",
			"value": "b7e1b208-147e-447c-9c84-15309be6807c",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Create Test - Full Data",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					},
					{
						"key": "X-API-Key",
						"value": "{{api_key}}"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"patient_id\": \"HN00100\",\n  \"patient_name\": \"JAIDEE^SOMCHAI\",\n  \"sex\": \"M\",\n  \"birth_date\": \"19800115\",\n  \"priority\": \"ROUTINE\",\n  \"ordering_physician\": \"Dr. Anupong\",\n  \"ordering_department\": \"Cardiology\",\n  \"patient_source\": \"Outpatient\",\n  \"clinical_info\": \"Chest pain, palpitation\",\n  \"phone\": \"0812345678\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/create-test",
					"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
					"path": ["api", "v1", "create-test"]
				},
				"description": "สร้าง ECG Test ใหม่ ส่งข้อมูลครบทุก field\n\n**Required fields:**\n- `patient_id` (HN)\n- `patient_name` (รูปแบบ DICOM: LASTNAME^FIRSTNAME)\n\n**Optional fields:**\n- `sex` — M, F, O\n- `birth_date` — YYYYMMDD\n- `accession_number` — ถ้าไม่ส่ง ระบบจะสร้างให้อัตโนมัติ\n- `scheduled_date` — YYYYMMDD (default: วันนี้)\n- `scheduled_time` — HHMMSS (default: เวลาปัจจุบัน)\n- `priority` — ROUTINE, URGENT\n- `ordering_physician`\n- `ordering_department`\n- `patient_source` — Outpatient, Inpatient, Emergency, Health Check\n- `bed_number`\n- `phone`\n- `clinical_info`\n- `procedure_desc`\n- `station_ae`\n- `station_name`"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Create Test - Minimal (Required Only)",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					},
					{
						"key": "X-API-Key",
						"value": "{{api_key}}"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"patient_id\": \"HN00200\",\n  \"patient_name\": \"KAEWDEE^SOMPORN\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/create-test",
					"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
					"path": ["api", "v1", "create-test"]
				},
				"description": "สร้าง ECG Test ส่งแค่ข้อมูลที่จำเป็น (HN + ชื่อ)\nระบบจะ auto-generate: accession number, scheduled date/time, และค่า default อื่นๆ"
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Create Test - Urgent Inpatient",
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					},
					{
						"key": "X-API-Key",
						"value": "{{api_key}}"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"patient_id\": \"HN00300\",\n  \"patient_name\": \"BOONMA^WICHAI\",\n  \"sex\": \"M\",\n  \"birth_date\": \"19560218\",\n  \"priority\": \"URGENT\",\n  \"ordering_physician\": \"Dr. Somkiat\",\n  \"ordering_department\": \"ICU\",\n  \"patient_source\": \"Inpatient\",\n  \"bed_number\": \"ICU-5\",\n  \"clinical_info\": \"Post MI day 3, chest pain recurrence\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/create-test",
					"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
					"path": ["api", "v1", "create-test"]
				},
				"description": "สร้าง ECG Test แบบ Urgent สำหรับผู้ป่วยใน (Inpatient)"
			},
			"response": []
		},
